        dc:description           "Figure 8. Coccidula rufa (Reitter) A tegmen, inner B tegmen, lateral C penis, lateral D male genital segment, dorsal E spermatheca. Scale bar: 500 µm (A-E)." , "Figure 7. Coccidula rufa (Reitter) SEM illustrations A body, dorsal B pronotum C head and prothorax, ventral D antenna E mesoventrite, metaventrite and ventrite 1 F ventrites 4 - 6, female. Scale bars: 1 mm (A); 500 µm (B, C, E, F); 400 µm (D)." , "Figure 1. Immature stages and habitus of adult species of Coccidula Kugelann A C. rufa larva B C. rufa pupa C C. lepida, dorsal D C. lepida, ventral E C. litophiloides F C. reitteri G C. rufa H C. scutellata A, B Gilles San Martin, Wikimedia Commons C, D Danny Haelewaters G, H Udo Schmidt. Scale bars: 1 mm (C-H)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554384" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554383" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554376" .

